
TOPIC: MAP/LMARGN

82          0052          LMARGN

Column of the left margin of text
(GR.0 or text window only).  Zero is
the value for the left edge of the
screen; LMARGN is initialized to
two. You can POKE the margin
locations to set them to your
specific program needs, such as POKE
82,10 to make the left margin start
ten locations from the edge of the
screen.

